info.name: Radioactive Sky - Roblox
info.description: This style is a follow up to a request. So the theme colo(u)rs aren't the best, if you got any suggestions I'll be sure to implement them if they are indeed better. Credits go to >sdlsgraphics< for this nice artwork inspired by Steven universe, I slightly edited the background to have more types of green. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads, or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. A disclaimer: all the translations I make are just Google translated, I ain't no multilingual savant, so if there are any readers who are proficient in the languages above, please do tell me where I've messed up. 7 December 2022 - Released. 1 July 2023 - Revamped style with new base code.
